# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  Environment Variables — Agent-Nuvira
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
#  Copy this file to .env and fill in your API keys:
#    cp .env.example .env
#    # Then edit .env with your keys
#
#  Without any keys, only local models (Ollama) are available.
#  Each provider below is optional — configure only the ones you use.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── Groq ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Fast LPU cloud inference. Free tier: ~30 req/min, 14400 req/day.
# Get your key: https://console.groq.com
# GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# ─── NVIDIA NIM ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NVIDIA NIM cloud or self-hosted inference. Free tier: 1000 req/day.
# Get your key: https://build.nvidia.com
# NVIDIA_NIM_API_KEY=nvapi-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# ─── Google Gemini ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Google Gemini API — strong reasoning, large context. Free tier: 60 req/min.
# Get your key: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSyxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# ─── OpenRouter ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Unified API — access 200+ models. $1 free trial credits.
# Get your key: https://openrouter.ai/keys
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# ─── Local Inference (Ollama) ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# When running with `docker compose --profile ollama up`, set OLLAMA_HOST
# to point to the companion container.
# OLLAMA_HOST=http://ollama:11434
